5
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:28,480
He Jinchen was in the room
for a long time.

6
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,640
He just came out.

7
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:32,799
Got it.

8
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:34,159
Keep watching.

9
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:38,920
- He Jinchen is such trash.
- Boss.

10
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,599
Please calm down.

11
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:43,319
Miss Su has to act as Mrs. He

12
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,200
and live with that family.

13
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:45,400
It's kind of unavoidable.

14
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:48,040
But with her moves,

15
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:49,239
her agility,

16
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,159
no one would...

17
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:50,719
Get lost!

18
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,120
Yes.

19
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:56,560
He Jinchen.

20
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:06,480
Jinchen,

21
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,280
mind if I have a drink here?

22
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:11,159
What's wrong?

23
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,680
Got yourself in trouble again?

24
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:16,199
Just woman trouble.

25
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,719
Niannian came home,

26
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:20,960
but she's always suspicious of me.

27
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:23,479
You know,

28
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:26,000
you should tone it down outside.

29
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,479
It's all just for fun.

30
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:30,879
Niannian stays home all day,

31
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,319
so she overthinks.

32
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:33,680
Qingmei is different.

33
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,840
She is doing great in her career.

34
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,919
She probably has no time
to suspect you, right?

35
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:40,000
What are you getting at?

36
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,439
Nothing.

37
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:46,439
She's just like a different person now.

38
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,360
Don't you find that strange?

39
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:54,000
She had a head injury
and lost her memory.

40
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:56,280
It is normal for her personality
to change a bit.

41
00:02:57,759 --> 00:02:58,439
Normal?

42
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:01,520
Even if someone loses their memory,

43
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,879
they don't turn into another person.

44
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,719
Jinchen,

45
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,479
aren't you worried

46
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:12,280
that she might not be Gu Qingmei?

47
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,159
You're talking nonsense again.

48
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:18,639
He Jinchuan,

49
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:21,280
if you keep running your mouth
about my wife,

50
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,759
I won't go easy on you.

51
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,000
Fine, fine.

52
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:26,520
I was just running my mouth.

53
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:28,439
Enjoy yourself. I'm heading back.

54
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,240
(Lab Report)
The bird's nest you brought

55
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,800
(Lab Report)
contains traces of thallium sulfate.

56
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:45,360
Thallium poisoning may
cause fatigue, hair loss,

57
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,240
stomach pain and nausea.

58
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,520
Prolonged use

59
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:49,879
may cause irreversible damage
to the body.

60
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:50,759
It can even be fatal.

61
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,080
I never thought

62
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,919
my caring husband

63
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:00,199
would actually want me dead.

64
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,599
Now he's not just after your life,

65
00:04:03,319 --> 00:04:04,680
