from your family too.

66
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,719
Why?

67
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,560
I treated him so well,

68
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:19,240
why is he doing this to me?

69
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:24,439
What do I do now?

70
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:26,519
In a marriage,

71
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,519
you either put up with it,

72
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:28,680
fight back,

73
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:29,839
or get out.

74
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,560
Which one will you choose?

75
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:38,360
I want a divorce.

76
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:40,360
I want him to lose everything.

77
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,279
Okay.

78
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,560
Let me help you.

79
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:49,839
Dear.

80
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,360
That project we invested in
went really well.

81
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,319
Maybe we should put in some more.

82
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:56,040
Sure.

83
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:56,720
Really?

84
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:01,000
No.

85
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,959
Last time,
I used the money without permission

86
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,120
and dad found out.

87
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,240
He froze all my accounts.

88
00:05:06,439 --> 00:05:08,079
What? Why?

89
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,360
He said

90
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:13,600
we don't have a sense for investments.

91
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,839
He told us not to invest recklessly.

92
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,040
We should just keep the family wealth.

93
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,439
I don't have a sense for investments?

94
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:22,959
Niannian, you have my word.

95
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:25,120
I will achieve something great.

96
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:26,639
I will prove everyone wrong.

97
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:32,740
(Dao Ba)

98
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,040
I have some work to deal with.

99
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:37,040
Finish your bird's nest.

100
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,399
Sleep well.

101
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:40,879
Good night.

102
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,360
Disgusting.

103
00:06:09,639 --> 00:06:10,480
Stop rushing me.

104
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,360
I am about to get a lot of money.

105
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,079
(Miss Su.)

106
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:24,000
(Meet me by the pool.)

107
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,519
(Sure.)

108
00:06:35,639 --> 00:06:36,959
What do you want this time?

109
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:39,120
I want fifty million right now.

110
00:06:40,079 --> 00:06:41,000
Or I will tell everyone

111
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:41,600
who you really are

112
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,720
and you'll lose everything.

113
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,720
I don't have that much money.

114
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:47,079
I just took over Gu Corporation.

115
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:48,759
Even my shares are limited by the will.

116
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,360
I can't get that much at once.

117
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,879
I don't believe you have nothing.

118
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,120
Just give me everything you have

119
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,439
right now!

120
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,600
All I have

121
00:07:00,439 --> 00:07:01,560
are those two sets of jewelry

122
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,040
your brother gave me.

123
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:04,600
I will bring them to you later.

124
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:07,839
Fine.

125
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:10,879
Hurry up and get the rest.

126
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:17,600
My previous sister-in-law

127
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,720
also used to give me jewelry
to pawn for cash.

128
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:21,519
She often...

129
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:22,360
What are you two doing?

130
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,079
Dear!

131
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:25,879
He Jinchuan, you trash!

132
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:27,240
Let me explain, dear!

133
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:27,959
Trash!

134
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,000
- Dear!
- Trash!

135
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:29,600
What are you doing?

136
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,040
- I will kill you!
- Dear!

137
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,800
Dear, just let me explain!

138
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,600
- I will kill you!
- Dear!

139
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,120
Dear, please listen to me!

140
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:33,839
Dear!

141
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,439
Trash!

142
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:40,920
Dear!

143
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,000
Calm down!

144
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,079
Niannian!

145
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,480
Calm down?

146
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,600
Don't you tell me!

147
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:48,279
Calm down?

148
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:48,879
Just listen!

149
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,600
No!

150
00:07:50,439 --> 00:07:51,279
- Go to hell!
- Dear!

151
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:52,759
Let me explain! Dear!

152
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:54,079
Niannian!

153
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,199
Niannian! Niannian!

154
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,399
I want a divorce!

155
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,920
Niannian! It wasn't me!

156
00:07:58,439 --> 00:07:58,879
It was her!

157
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,120
She seduced me!

158
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:00,920
Niannian!

159
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:02,600
I stayed loyal to you!

160
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,879
Why does every woman
throw herself at you?

161
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:07,600
Dear!

162
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,240
I was wrong.

163
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:10,279
I know I messed up.

164
00:08:10,439 --> 00:08:10,920
Dear!

165
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,279
I really know I messed up.

166
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,040
Dear!

167
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,639
I...

168
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:14,560
I...

169
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,439
Just give me one more chance.

170
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,439
I can't live without you.

171
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,920
Fine. If we're not divorcing,

172
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,720
then you'll sign an agreement.

173
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,079
If you cheat again,

174
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,360
you walk away with nothing.

175
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:26,639
For you,

176
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:27,920
I'd even give up my life.

177
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:32,120
I doubt you'll pass the test.

178
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,440
Sign the property agreement.

179
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,039
I will never divorce you.

180
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:42,639
I will definitely pass the test.

181
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:46,740
(He Jinchuan)

182
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:50,720
Dear.

183
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,120
I really know I messed up.

184
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:52,960
Dear.

185
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,080
Just give me one more chance.

186
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:55,120
I can't live without you.

187
00:08:55,879 --> 00:08:58,080
Now I finally see

188
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,039
what disgust

189
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,159
and shamelessness really mean.

190
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,919
So what's your next move?

191
00:09:05,679 --> 00:09:07,279
I am going to show the whole world

192
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:09,559
what He Jinchuan is truly like.

193
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,240
Need my help?

194
00:09:12,159 --> 00:09:12,639
No.

195
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,159
You have already helped me a lot.

196
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:15,600
Besides,

197
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,879
when it comes to taking down that trash,

198
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,600
it is more satisfying to do it myself.

199
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:19,799
Alright.

200
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:24,639
Do you think He Jinchen
might be the same?

201
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,440
Am I interrupting a girls' party?

202
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:31,159
No, I was just leaving.

203
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,039
Qingmei,

204
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:35,399
I think he's hotter than your husband.

205
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,759
Enough about your pretty-boy obsession.

206
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:39,960
No more being so lovesick.

207
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:41,600
That won't happen.

208
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:44,519
But if I do date again,

209
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:45,679
he still has to be handsome.

210
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:47,440
Fair enough.

211
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:48,399
- Bye.
- Bye.

212
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,480
She is still not that smart,

213
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,480
is she?

214
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:00,000
I think she's adorable.

215
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:03,200
It means her family raised her well.

216
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,039
She's innocent.

217
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:05,039
Otherwise,

218
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,879
she wouldn't have been fooled
by He Jinchuan.

219
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:12,480
Both brothers are trash.

220
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,399
To be fair,

221
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,840
He Jinchen isn't that bad.

222
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,799
He is not that bad?

223
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:24,879
Watch it, we're still outside.

224
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:27,080
I'm still the eldest daughter-in-law.

225
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:29,120
We should keep a low profile,

226
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,799
so He Jinchen doesn't get suspicious.

227
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:34,919
I feel like your secret lover.

228
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:38,519
Well, keep it up then.

229
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,240
We're almost there.

230
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,720
I have some business at the resort.
I need to go.

231
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:42,759
Bye.

232
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,399
Sir, your coffee.

233
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:56,399
Wait.

234
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,399
Anything else I can do for you?

235
00:10:58,919 --> 00:10:59,480
Hey, pretty.

236
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,120
Can I get your WeChat?

237
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,799
Sir, I'm at work.

238
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,600
Please show some respect.

239
00:11:04,159 --> 00:11:04,759
Come on.

240
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:06,360
Let's be friends.

241
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:06,960
What are you doing!

242
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,440
Let me see your name.

243
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:08,120
Let go of me!

244
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:09,519
Let me see!

245
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:11,440
Hey!

246
00:11:12,039 --> 00:11:12,720
- What are you doing?
- Let go!

247
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,919
None of your business!

248
00:11:17,039 --> 00:11:18,360
Madam Gu, are you okay?

249
00:11:18,679 --> 00:11:19,639
It's got nothing to do with me!

250
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:20,759
You ran into me!

251
00:11:20,919 --> 00:11:22,200
Why do you have to be so nosy?

252
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:22,799
Security!

253
00:11:23,159 --> 00:11:23,759
Security!

254
00:11:24,759 --> 00:11:25,519
Will they listen to you?

255
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,399
Get this man out.

256
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:27,639
He's banned from the resort.

257
00:11:27,879 --> 00:11:28,360
Yes, madam.

258
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:29,159
Move!

259
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:30,799
Who are you to keep me out?

260
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,080
I want to see your manager!

261
00:11:32,159 --> 00:11:33,159
I want to file a complaint!

262
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,120
Let me go!

263
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:34,960
Are you okay?

264
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:35,879
I am fine.

265
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:45,320
Boss.

266
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:46,879
Boss.

267
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,799
Miss Su got hurt at the resort.

268
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:51,840
Boss.

269
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:53,480
That's what you are wearing?

270
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,039
The power of love.

271
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:27,600
What brings you here?

272
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:31,559
I heard you got hurt
defending your staff.

273
00:12:32,279 --> 00:12:33,279
As your business partner,

274
00:12:34,279 --> 00:12:36,120
I should come check on you.

275
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,399
It was just...

276
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:38,840
No...

277
00:12:39,279 --> 00:12:41,080
No... Put me down!

278
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,039
What are you doing?

279
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:44,639
No...

280
00:12:47,759 --> 00:12:48,960
I am really fine.

281
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,279
It's nothing serious.

282
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,639
Why didn't you tell me you were hurt?

283
00:12:53,759 --> 00:12:54,720
What am I to you?

284
00:12:58,759 --> 00:12:59,559
A business partner.

285
00:13:00,799 --> 00:13:01,639
Your words.

286
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,159
To keep my business growing,

287
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,240
I need to look after you.

288
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:09,559
Turn around.

289
00:13:10,919 --> 00:13:11,360
No...

290
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,320
What are you doing?

291
00:13:14,879 --> 00:13:15,360
Does it hurt?

292
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,360
No...

293
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,320
It didn't hurt

294
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,120
until you pressed it.

295
00:13:24,519 --> 00:13:25,360
Looks like you hurt your back.

296
00:13:26,159 --> 00:13:27,519
Take some time to rest.

297
00:13:29,559 --> 00:13:30,039
I...

298
00:13:30,559 --> 00:13:32,200
I still have a ton of work to do.

299
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,039
I will handle it.

300
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:40,080
I'm not paralyzed.

301
00:13:41,039 --> 00:13:42,360
Back injuries are no joke.

302
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,200
If you don't take care,

303
00:13:44,519 --> 00:13:45,960
you could have permanent issues.

304
00:13:50,559 --> 00:13:51,120
Get up.

305
00:13:51,919 --> 00:13:52,440
Why?

306
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:53,879
Bathroom break.

307
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:55,960
Let me help you.

308
00:13:59,279 --> 00:13:59,799
Slow down.

309
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:03,039
It's not that serious.

310
00:14:04,559 --> 00:14:05,000
You...

311
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,679
Mr. Mu, perhaps you should

312
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,759
watch your behavior.

313
00:14:10,399 --> 00:14:11,440
She is my wife,

314
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:12,639
your sister-in-law.

315
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,159
Sister-in-law?

316
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:14,759
Mr. Mu.

317
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,039
Thank you for your concern.

318
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,519
My back feels much better now.

319
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,559
Then I'll stay tonight

320
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,159
and take care of you properly.

321
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:25,039
I don't need you.

322
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,240
If you insist on staying,

323
00:14:26,519 --> 00:14:27,279
there's an empty room next door.

324
00:14:27,919 --> 00:14:28,840
I am your husband.

325
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:30,360
I should take care of you.

326
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,279
Husband?

327
00:14:31,679 --> 00:14:32,840
We've been married for years.

328
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,399
Have you ever taken care of me once?

329
00:15:01,700 --> 00:15:06,460
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

330
00:15:06,460 --> 00:15:11,300
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

331
00:15:11,300 --> 00:15:15,860
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

332
00:15:15,860 --> 00:15:20,780
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

333
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:24,580
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

334
00:15:24,580 --> 00:15:29,380
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

335
00:15:29,380 --> 00:15:32,220
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

336
00:15:32,220 --> 00:15:34,900
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

337
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:40,820
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

338
00:15:41,220 --> 00:15:48,020
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

339
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:52,980
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

340
00:15:53,140 --> 00:15:59,940
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

341
00:16:00,260 --> 00:16:07,060
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

342
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:11,740
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

343
00:16:11,740 --> 00:16:15,100
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

344
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:22,020
♪Right as I confess my love♪
